表的代码预览业务-公告表

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('busi_notice')
and type = 'U')
drop table busi_notice
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: busi_notice */
/*==============================================================*/
create table busi_notice (
NoticeID int identity,
Content varchar(3000) not null,
Status int not null,
AppAdmin int not null,
Type int not null,
AppTime datetime not null default getdate(),
IsDel bit not null default 0,
constraint PK_BUSI_NOTICE primary key (NoticeID)
)
go

if exists (select 1 from sys.extended_properties
where major_id = object_id('busi_notice') and minor_id = 0)
begin

'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'busi_notice'

end
